OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1780902267
OL,3,CBath adventurer becomes first British
OL,4,Cwoman to cross Atlantic by balloon
OL,6,FA British adventurer has crossed the
OL,7,FAtlantic Ocean by hydrogen balloon.
OL,9,FAlicia Hempleman-Adams, from Bath,
OL,10,Flanded with her teammates Bert Padelt
OL,11,Fand Peter Cuneo in Bastendorf,
OL,12,FLuxembourg, at 5.58am UTC on Sunday.
OL,14,FThe team said Ms Hempleman-Adams has
OL,15,Fbecome only the second woman in
OL,16,Fhistory ` and the first from Britain `
OL,17,Fto cross the Atlantic Ocean by gas
OL,18,Fballoon.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
