PN,43102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1780902267
OL,3,CBath adventurer becomes first British
OL,4,Cwoman to cross Atlantic by balloon
OL,6,FThe crossing was made on the Atlantic
OL,7,FExplorer, an open-basket gas balloon
OL,8,Fwhich launched from Presque Isle,
OL,9,FMaine, on Thursday at 6.08am UTC.
OL,11,FThe team added that their mission was
OL,12,Fto attempt the first successful manned
OL,13,Ftransoceanic flight in a balloon using
OL,14,Fhydrogen gas as its sole onboard
OL,15,Fsource of lift.
OL,17,FDuring the journey, the team flew at
OL,18,Fan average altitude of 14,000 feet,
OL,19,Fspending 70 hours in the air, with
OL,20,Fspeeds of up to 100 kilometres per
OL,21,Fhour.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
