CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1780902267
OL,3,CBath adventurer becomes first British
OL,4,Cwoman to cross Atlantic by balloon
OL,6,FSpeaking after the landing, Ms
OL,7,FHempleman-Adams said: "I'm incredibly
OL,8,Fproud that we completed the crossing
OL,9,Fand made it safely across to
OL,10,FLuxembourg."
OL,12,FShe added: "There were times when we
OL,13,Fthought we might not make it.
OL,15,F"Flying through rain caused ice to
OL,16,Fbuild up on the balloon, which made
OL,17,Fconditions extremely difficult and
OL,18,Fadded real jeopardy to the flight.
OL,26,@oD@WOUrD@LO]tD@LOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
