OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1780902267
OL,3,CBath adventurer becomes first British
OL,4,Cwoman to cross Atlantic by balloon
OL,6,F"It was an extraordinary team effort
OL,7,Fto keep going and bring the balloon
OL,8,Fsafely across the Atlantic.
OL,10,F"I feel very fortunate to have had the
OL,11,Fopportunity to learn so much from two
OL,12,Fworld-class pilots."
OL,14,FMs Hempleman-Adams's father, Sir David
OL,15,FHempleman-Adams, previously completed
OL,16,Fthe Atlantic journey solo, also in an
OL,17,Fopen basket.
OL,19,FSir David said: "I am enormously proud
OL,20,Fof Alicia.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUtD@TO]{D@QOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
