OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1780902267
OL,3,CBath adventurer becomes first British
OL,4,Cwoman to cross Atlantic by balloon
OL,6,F"I know first-hand just how tough an
OL,7,FAtlantic crossing in an open basket
OL,8,Fcan be, and to complete it in such
OL,9,Fchallenging conditions is a remarkable
OL,10,Fachievement."
OL,12,FMs Hempleman-Adams was made an MBE for
OL,13,Fservices to hot air ballooning in the
OL,14,FKing's Birthday Honours in 2024.
